tptNgfwCluster.name: tptNgfwCluster

revisions.description: Updated copyright information. Minor MIB syntax fixes.
Initial version of NGFW Cluster MIB.

tptNgfwCluster.description: This MIB defines TippingPoint Next-Generation Firewall Cluster and HA management information. Cluster information includes details on configuration, cluster membership, device's role (active/passive) in a cluster as well as overall health and status for monitoring purposes. High-availability information provides details on the device's membership in Fail-over Groups and the status of feature state synchronization across nodes in the group and cluster.
